bring leaf pieces to the nest. These ants are so industrious that, scaled to human dimensions, each worker runs the equivalent of four-minute mile for 30-some miles (48 km.), with 500 }{\fs22\lang2057\langfe1055\langnp2057\insrsid2822717\charrsid9585949 
